  Make new folder             ----                 $  mkdir ~/Downloads/new-folder
(Inside Downloads)
                                                 
                                                 
 Make new folder with       ----                 $  sudo mkdir ~/Downloads/new-folder
 write protected

Delete any folder           ----                 $  rm -R ~/Downloads/new-folder

Delete file named 'x.txt'   ----                 $  rm x.txt

Create empty file 'x.txt'  
under '/var/wwww/html'           ----            $  sudo touch /var/www/html/x.txt

copy one file content in another file      ------  $ cp first_file another_file


copy any file in any folder where folder's path is : /any_folder/          --------     $ cp any_file /any_folder/

